    <item>
      <title>KKR 将收购 Global Atlantic 保险公司剩余 37% 的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-11-29/kkr-to-acquire-remaining-37-of-insurer-global-atlantic-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[KKR &amp; Co. 将收购其尚未拥有的 Global Atlantic 剩余 37% 的股份，并支付约 27 亿美元现金以扩大其在保险领域的投资，以推动资产和费用增长。 KKR 联合首席执行官 Scott Nuttall 与 Sonali Basak 讨论了该交易。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-11-29/kkr-to-acquire-remaining-37-of-insurer-global-atlantic-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 12:42:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易商押注南非将比预期更快降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-29/traders-revise-south-africa-rate-cut-bets-as-credit-growth-slows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在流入经济的资金量和私营部门贷款录得近两年来最弱增长后，交易员将南非首次降息的押注提前至 2024 年 3 月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-29/traders-revise-south-africa-rate-cut-bets-as-credit-growth-slows</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 12:27:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>7万亿美元的ETF繁荣再次因愚蠢的股票走势而受到指责</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-29/the-7-trillion-etf-boom-gets-blamed-again-for-dumb-stock-moves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这是对被动投资热潮的最新批评：新的学术研究声称，华尔街追逐指数的资金源源不断地涌入，正在扭曲股价并引发极端的市场波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-29/the-7-trillion-etf-boom-gets-blamed-again-for-dumb-stock-moves</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 12:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
